sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as PackageUnlink
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant Composer

    User->>CLI: orbit package unlink package app
    CLI->>CLI: Build app path from ~/projects/
    
    CLI->>FS: Check appPath exists
    alt App not found
        FS-->>CLI: false
        CLI-->>User: Error - App not found
    else App exists
        FS-->>CLI: true
        CLI->>Composer: composer unlink package
        Note over Composer: Run in appPath directory
        
        alt Unlink failed
            Composer-->>CLI: error
            CLI-->>User: Error - Failed to unlink
        else Unlink succeeded
            Composer-->>CLI: success
            CLI-->>User: Package unlinked from app
        end
    end
